WEBVTT

01:38.320 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 23

01:46.440 --> 01:48.040
You're online at last, Weiguang!

01:48.280 --> 01:51.440
I'm waiting at the old place
in Jinling City. Come soon!

02:36.680 --> 02:39.680
You're here, Weiguang!
I waited for you for so long.

02:39.760 --> 02:40.680
Why did you wait for me?

02:41.640 --> 02:44.800
No reason. I have a surprise for you.

02:50.440 --> 02:53.120
- What?
- It's a gift for you.

02:54.200 --> 02:55.160
Check it out.

03:08.600 --> 03:11.200
I finally get to do something for you.

03:11.400 --> 03:13.320
Are you so moved, that you could cry?

03:15.440 --> 03:16.560
WEIGUANG

03:18.320 --> 03:19.400
It's engraved on the back, too.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.720
HUANXI

03:25.920 --> 03:27.480
You can call it Weiguang.

03:27.560 --> 03:29.440
Or you can call it Huanxi.

03:31.680 --> 03:35.200
You can also call it Huanxi Weiguang.

03:35.480 --> 03:39.080
I made it myself, after putting so much
into blacksmithing.

03:39.200 --> 03:40.440
I'm super lucky, too.

03:40.600 --> 03:42.880
I got OP equipment at the first try.
It's for you.

03:48.120 --> 03:51.000
It's such a nice sword. May I try it?

03:51.360 --> 03:54.520
Sure, let's have three duels,
to try the sword.

04:08.760 --> 04:11.520
It is a nice sword. I like it.

04:12.640 --> 04:15.200
You know, Weiguang,
when you said you liked it,

04:15.280 --> 04:18.320
all the hard work I put into the sword
was totally worth it.

04:38.120 --> 04:39.640
- Again?
- Again.

05:00.520 --> 05:01.480
Are you okay?

05:02.560 --> 05:03.400
Yes.

05:20.400 --> 05:23.480
I have a gift for you, too, Huantian Xidi.

05:32.160 --> 05:34.800
This move is called break up and shut up.

05:37.760 --> 05:42.800
Bei Weiwei, I, Cao Guang, have had
enough of your phony romance scheme.

05:57.120 --> 05:58.880
During my duels with the Xiaoyus,

05:58.960 --> 06:02.320
I totally channeled you.
I was so ferocious.

06:02.440 --> 06:04.640
It gives me such thrill,
thinking back on it.

06:05.680 --> 06:07.800
Sounds like you showed
a tenth of my prowess.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.240
That much?

06:18.400 --> 06:21.800
But, would Erxi be mad at me,

06:22.160 --> 06:23.760
if I told her about this?

06:25.560 --> 06:29.280
No, no. My friend Erxi is very agreeable.

06:33.320 --> 06:34.160
Stop the car!

06:40.320 --> 06:43.320
I decided, I should buy a cake
to appease her.

06:47.120 --> 06:48.280
Welcome.

06:54.240 --> 06:55.640
It's so expensive.

07:05.320 --> 07:08.880
Let me borrow some money.
I'll pay you back, when I get paid.

07:15.240 --> 07:16.280
Why are you giving me so much?

07:17.160 --> 07:18.400
Use it to appease me.

07:26.720 --> 07:29.120
I'll take the chocolate cake.

07:31.000 --> 07:32.520
This, too. Wrap it for me.

07:35.160 --> 07:36.360
Thank you.

07:39.760 --> 07:40.680
It's to appease you.

07:41.000 --> 07:42.440
I don't like cakes.

07:44.640 --> 07:45.920
You're so hard to appease.

07:47.480 --> 07:48.400
And it's too small.

07:50.480 --> 07:53.520
Too small? Here's what you don't get.

07:53.680 --> 07:54.560
You gave me 1,000 bucks.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.680
I can only buy a few big cakes.

07:57.800 --> 07:59.280
But, if I choose small cakes,

07:59.360 --> 08:02.400
I can buy one many times.
Which would you want?

08:06.800 --> 08:07.680
I want them all.

08:08.880 --> 08:09.720
Greedy.

08:11.560 --> 08:12.400
Let's go.

08:18.640 --> 08:20.040
She's not back yet?

08:35.120 --> 08:36.360
Erxi?

08:41.280 --> 08:45.360
What's wrong? What happened?

08:46.320 --> 08:47.840
Come on... get up.

08:50.960 --> 08:54.120
I know, I'll get you
some water with brown sugar.

08:58.840 --> 08:59.680
By the way, Erxi,

09:00.600 --> 09:03.360
I want to apologize to you.

09:04.640 --> 09:07.960
Those girls who tormented you at work

09:08.680 --> 09:10.520
were players in "A Chinese Ghost Story."

09:10.920 --> 09:14.240
They thought you were me, so...

09:15.920 --> 09:17.440
sorry, Erxi.

09:17.720 --> 09:19.960
You suffered because of me.

09:21.280 --> 09:22.720
They thought I was you?

09:24.280 --> 09:26.560
Maybe it's because you said
you were Luwei Weiwei,

09:26.640 --> 09:28.000
at the internship interview.

09:28.920 --> 09:31.160
Don't worry, though.
I got them back for you.

09:31.480 --> 09:34.720
I didn't tell them you were my roommate.

09:34.800 --> 09:36.040
So they won't bug you again.

09:44.520 --> 09:47.960
This cake is for you,
as a token of my sincere apologies.

09:48.040 --> 09:49.640
Your Highness, please accept it.

09:57.880 --> 10:00.560
This move is called break-up and shut up.

10:01.360 --> 10:05.920
Bei Weiwei, I, Cao Guang, have had
enough of your phony romance scheme.

10:11.720 --> 10:13.080
It's your favorite cake.

10:15.000 --> 10:15.920
Get out!

10:18.520 --> 10:19.720
- Erxi?
- I said, get out!

11:00.640 --> 11:04.840
Why are you moody, Yiran? Are you upset?

11:05.160 --> 11:06.920
What is it? You can tell me.

11:09.680 --> 11:11.720
Why would I be upset?

11:12.440 --> 11:14.120
I was just thinking,

11:15.600 --> 11:18.920
maybe I should have a new goal in life.

11:19.920 --> 11:22.360
Relationship-wise or career-wise?

11:25.520 --> 11:26.640
Are you done?

11:27.680 --> 11:30.560
Almost. This pasta is so good.

11:30.640 --> 11:31.760
I want to finish it.

11:33.440 --> 11:37.520
I'll settle the bill first. Check, please!

11:38.360 --> 11:40.480
Do you have membership?
You can get a discount.

11:41.200 --> 11:42.040
I do.

11:43.280 --> 11:44.960
It's okay. Just settle the bill.

11:47.920 --> 11:49.080
Let me accumulate points.

11:52.680 --> 11:55.520
There's a photo of my card in my phone.

12:01.040 --> 12:01.880
What's wrong?

12:08.480 --> 12:11.000
You only need the card number
to accumulate points.

12:29.400 --> 12:30.680
Who told you my heart's broken?

12:31.160 --> 12:33.920
I'm just ashamed for having poor judgment.

12:35.200 --> 12:37.000
I always thought I was smart,

12:37.360 --> 12:40.960
yet I still failed to see
what a hussy Bei Weiwei is.

12:41.480 --> 12:44.400
Let the past rest.
A guy like you can have the pick

12:44.480 --> 12:47.400
of any of those pretty and innocent girls

12:47.600 --> 12:49.200
of the Foreign Languages Department.

12:49.880 --> 12:53.960
Who cares for those high-IQ,
low-EQ science and engineering girls?

12:54.400 --> 12:57.800
She's such a good actress.
How could she have low EQ?

12:58.440 --> 13:02.360
True, she's totally into you in the game,

13:02.880 --> 13:05.760
yet in real life, she's sweet on Xiao Nai.

13:06.080 --> 13:09.600
She deserves an Oscar
for best leading actress, no?

13:18.120 --> 13:20.080
What's the card number?

13:20.920 --> 13:22.040
I'll just pay.

13:22.960 --> 13:24.680
That will be 339 RMB.

13:25.560 --> 13:26.560
Just a moment.

13:32.120 --> 13:35.160
I nearly choked to death on that bite.

13:38.720 --> 13:40.000
What are you keeping from me?

13:41.800 --> 13:43.840
What can I be keeping from you?

13:47.240 --> 13:49.000
What about the video on your phone?

13:58.000 --> 14:00.000
Let me explain, Yiran.

14:00.080 --> 14:01.200
There's nothing to explain.

14:01.280 --> 14:03.760
I thought you were a friend.
I tell you everything.

14:03.840 --> 14:06.560
I can't believe you kept
something that big from me.

14:08.120 --> 14:11.440
It's not what you think.
I' wanted to tell you,

14:11.520 --> 14:12.920
but I was afraid you'd be upset.

14:13.000 --> 14:16.480
You moved out of the dorm.
I never got a chance to tell you.

14:17.600 --> 14:19.880
What about later?
Why didn't you tell me later?

14:21.920 --> 14:26.640
Didn't you say, you gave up on him?
I didn't want to mention it after that.

14:27.480 --> 14:29.440
It's so important!
How could you not mention it?

14:30.640 --> 14:32.000
A nice guy like Xiao Nai

14:32.240 --> 14:35.040
is being lied to by
a two-timing Bei Weiwei!

14:35.200 --> 14:36.680
How could you not tell me?

14:38.960 --> 14:41.400
I was going to post the video online,

14:41.480 --> 14:44.120
and expose Bei Weiwei
for who she is, but...

14:45.240 --> 14:47.440
Why don't we post it now?

14:47.520 --> 14:51.080
It's summer break,
but people still follow Lord's news.

14:51.520 --> 14:54.160
Let's post it now and expose Bei Weiwei.

14:54.240 --> 14:55.240
No.

14:56.240 --> 14:59.280
If we do that,
Xiao Nai would lose face, too.

14:59.560 --> 15:01.080
I don't want him to get hurt.

15:02.520 --> 15:04.720
You'd keep him in the dark?

15:05.200 --> 15:06.480
That's even worse!

15:11.160 --> 15:13.600
Send me the video, now.
I'll show Xiao Nai.

15:14.160 --> 15:16.160
Okay, I'll send you the video.

15:17.840 --> 15:20.160
I had no idea Bei Weiwei is like that.

15:20.280 --> 15:22.320
My goodwill was totally pointless.

15:22.400 --> 15:25.520
Plus, a girl like her
isn't good enough for Xiao Nai.

15:25.600 --> 15:27.440
I shouldn't let her have him.

15:28.600 --> 15:31.120
When will you tell him, Yiran?

15:31.480 --> 15:33.120
I can't wait for another minute.

15:55.200 --> 15:56.040
Hello?

15:58.120 --> 16:00.400
Hello? Is this Xiao Nai?

16:01.280 --> 16:03.320
Yes, and you are?

16:03.760 --> 16:05.640
Hi, Mr. Xiao. I'm Meng Yiran.

16:07.360 --> 16:09.560
Hi, what's going on?

16:10.080 --> 16:13.640
There's something about Bei Weiwei
that you should know.

16:13.920 --> 16:16.000
I think it's best that I tell you.

16:16.760 --> 16:19.320
Why don't we meet at a cafe?

16:19.400 --> 16:20.520
I'm not interested.

16:24.800 --> 16:26.640
Hello? Hello?

16:47.760 --> 16:48.680
Xiao Nai!

16:50.160 --> 16:51.040
Uncle Li.

16:51.280 --> 16:53.400
- Are your parents back?
- Not yet.

16:53.720 --> 16:56.640
This mission is tougher.
They may stay for a month or two.

16:58.320 --> 16:59.480
You're still living off campus?

16:59.880 --> 17:01.480
Yes, but it's not far.

17:09.040 --> 17:12.160
- I'll get going, Uncle Li.
- Okay. See you.

17:28.640 --> 17:31.400
Mr. Xiao Nai...

17:34.680 --> 17:38.440
I... heard you jog around here.

17:38.520 --> 17:39.600
So I came to check it out,

17:40.280 --> 17:42.040
and I found you.

17:42.240 --> 17:43.800
If there's nothing else, excuse me.

17:43.880 --> 17:45.480
Wait!

17:47.160 --> 17:49.480
Why did you hang up on me?

17:50.480 --> 17:52.160
I don't want a third party

17:52.760 --> 17:54.400
to tell me things about my girlfriend.

17:56.000 --> 17:57.680
Not even this?

17:59.720 --> 18:02.360
I'm just ashamed for having poor judgment.

18:02.440 --> 18:04.040
I always thought I was smart,

18:04.120 --> 18:07.440
yet I still failed to see
what a hussy Bei Weiwei is.

18:07.520 --> 18:10.760
- Let the past rest.
- When my roommate took this video,

18:10.840 --> 18:13.080
she was going to post it
on the school forum.

18:13.160 --> 18:15.760
I stopped her, because I thought,

18:15.840 --> 18:19.200
no matter what a girl has done
in the past,

18:19.440 --> 18:23.480
the damage would be too great for her,
if this video gets published

18:23.640 --> 18:25.360
and everyone finds out.

18:25.800 --> 18:28.520
But, I don't want you to be lied to.

18:28.880 --> 18:31.160
We're already a couple in the game,

18:31.240 --> 18:33.280
yet she's dating Xiao Nai in real life.

18:33.760 --> 18:35.280
Does she think it's a game,
so it doesn't count?

18:35.360 --> 18:37.200
Does she think it's a game,
so she can toy with someone's heart?

19:14.440 --> 19:15.320
Oh, no!

19:17.480 --> 19:19.360
Looks like Erxi is really mad.

19:22.200 --> 19:24.680
But it's not like her to get so worked up.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.040
Hello?

19:48.840 --> 19:51.360
I'm downstairs. Come have breakfast.

20:02.160 --> 20:04.400
Such urgent business so early?

20:04.480 --> 20:06.920
Yes, I'm deleting trash.

20:26.880 --> 20:30.360
Where's the video? Did Yiran delete it?

20:37.200 --> 20:39.040
Your roommate got mad anyway?

20:40.600 --> 20:42.040
You can tell?

20:43.480 --> 20:47.000
Normally, Erxi wouldn't get mad
over something like this.

20:48.040 --> 20:51.240
Did the Xiaoyus do something worse to her?

20:51.480 --> 20:53.320
Looks like I let them off too easily.

20:57.920 --> 21:02.760
Weiwei, I thought about it for a while.
There's something you should know.

21:04.320 --> 21:05.160
What?

21:13.400 --> 21:15.800
- Take a look.
- What's this?

21:20.760 --> 21:23.040
We're already a couple in the game,

21:23.120 --> 21:25.160
yet she's dating Xiao Nai in real life.

21:25.640 --> 21:27.160
Does she think it's a game,
so it doesn't count?

21:27.240 --> 21:28.800
Does she think it's a game,
so she can toy with someone's heart?

21:31.960 --> 21:35.560
That's not true.
I don't know why he'd say that.

21:35.800 --> 21:38.640
He did confess his love for me,
but I turned him down then and there.

21:39.280 --> 21:41.560
There's no way
I'd string him along in the game.

21:44.560 --> 21:46.960
How could he make up something like that?

21:47.720 --> 21:48.840
It's awful!

21:49.360 --> 21:50.200
Delete it.

21:52.040 --> 21:52.880
What?

21:54.400 --> 21:57.720
Meng Yiran came to me with this video,
this morning.

21:57.880 --> 21:59.880
She said her roommate captured
the moment by accident.

22:00.640 --> 22:02.600
I deleted the video on her phone,

22:02.800 --> 22:04.680
and made a copy for myself.

22:04.920 --> 22:06.320
This should be the last copy.

22:07.440 --> 22:10.960
Meng Yiran? Why would she...

22:15.760 --> 22:19.480
Weiwei, perhaps telling you this

22:19.920 --> 22:21.040
would add to your woes,

22:22.520 --> 22:26.200
but I thought, maybe you'd want to

22:26.640 --> 22:28.160
handle this yourself.

22:40.160 --> 22:41.960
You should've handled this yourself,

22:42.880 --> 22:45.080
but there are too many busybodies around.

22:45.800 --> 22:47.920
I thought it best to get it over with.

22:52.600 --> 22:54.360
- Xiao Nai?
- Yes?

22:56.000 --> 22:57.240
I'm suddenly reminded of someone.

22:58.760 --> 22:59.600
Who?

23:00.640 --> 23:05.240
His name is Yixiao Naihe. Do you know him?

23:06.720 --> 23:09.400
I think you're a lot like him.

23:11.400 --> 23:14.040
Is that so? I don't know him well.

23:14.280 --> 23:15.680
When do I get to meet him?

23:24.920 --> 23:25.920
Now.

23:39.160 --> 23:42.520
Send me a copy of the video.
I'll confront Cao Guang.

23:42.600 --> 23:44.920
He's smeared my name again and again.
I've had it.

23:45.400 --> 23:46.280
Again and again?

23:48.200 --> 23:51.480
Yes. You know that
I'm the tutor of Xiaoyang?

23:51.880 --> 23:55.600
He took photos of Xiaoyang's mother
giving me a ride back to school,

23:57.000 --> 23:58.600
and insinuated I was with a rich guy.

24:00.640 --> 24:04.160
Thankfully, he at least blurred my face.

24:04.560 --> 24:06.040
Otherwise I'd never be able to
explain myself.

24:07.840 --> 24:10.440
Now, he's calling me a two-timer.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.360
I don't know
what I've done to deserve this.

24:13.560 --> 24:14.520
Do you need to me go with you?

24:16.840 --> 24:17.800
No.

24:18.120 --> 24:22.000
Your prowess is too great.
I can handle this myself.

24:24.120 --> 24:26.280
When Erxi calms down,

24:27.040 --> 24:29.400
I'll ask her for Cao Guang's number.

24:30.000 --> 24:32.360
I'll get a burlap sack
and a wooden club first.

24:32.920 --> 24:34.560
If you're going to fight,
you should bring me.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.040
You'll help me?

24:38.520 --> 24:41.480
No way. I'd just take you there.

24:41.880 --> 24:44.720
I'd only jump in, if you can't handle it.

24:49.600 --> 24:52.760
I'm swinging by Xiaoyang's place
this afternoon.

24:52.880 --> 24:53.720
Why?

24:55.400 --> 24:57.840
He came back from his summer vacation.

24:57.920 --> 25:01.000
He wants to give me a gift.
I nearly forgot.

25:01.640 --> 25:03.680
Okay, I'll take you there.

25:23.320 --> 25:25.360
You're a good kitty,

25:26.000 --> 25:29.320
but I have to leave you,
just when I've fallen for you.

25:30.520 --> 25:32.360
When your real owner is back,

25:32.440 --> 25:34.400
I won't care for you anymore.

25:36.040 --> 25:40.680
Will you miss me? Or will you forget me?

25:50.760 --> 25:52.720
You're here! I came back early.

25:53.640 --> 25:55.960
I'm surprised
that you're quite responsible.

25:56.360 --> 25:58.640
Thanks for keeping Coffee company
every day.

26:02.720 --> 26:04.880
Since you're back.
I won't come anymore. Bye.

26:04.960 --> 26:08.640
Wait! What's the hurry? Hold on a second.

26:18.920 --> 26:21.680
Don't get sentimental.
It's just a small thank-you gift.

26:22.120 --> 26:24.520
Is it good enough
for a foodaholic like you?

26:26.280 --> 26:28.080
Who told you I like chocolate?

26:28.320 --> 26:32.320
You can give it to whomever you want.
I don't want it!

26:53.120 --> 26:55.360
What's wrong with Erxi, Coffee?

26:55.440 --> 26:59.320
She turned down chocolate.
Did she swallow a nuclear bomb?

26:59.600 --> 27:00.720
Why is she fuming?

27:05.880 --> 27:08.360
Fine. I'll give it to someone else.

27:20.840 --> 27:21.680
I'll be right back.

27:45.640 --> 27:46.480
Stop there!

27:48.640 --> 27:49.840
What else do you want?

27:50.720 --> 27:51.800
Why are you here?

27:52.920 --> 27:54.080
I'm Xiaoyang's language tutor.

27:54.840 --> 27:57.600
You tutor Xiaoyang?
How come I had no idea?

27:58.920 --> 28:00.480
Since our first meeting,

28:00.560 --> 28:02.560
I managed to get on his good side
and became his tutor.

28:02.840 --> 28:05.200
I asked him to keep it from you,
to surprise you.

28:06.720 --> 28:09.560
Bei Weiwei, you must be relishing this.

28:09.640 --> 28:12.760
I've gone the whole nine yards
to please you, yet you take me for a fool.

28:13.880 --> 28:18.280
What are you talking about?
What would I be relishing?

28:18.920 --> 28:21.920
You better explain this first.
What's this video about?

28:22.720 --> 28:23.560
What video?

28:37.480 --> 28:39.760
We're already a couple in the game,

28:39.840 --> 28:41.880
yet she's dating Xiao Nai in real life.

28:42.360 --> 28:43.760
Does she think it's a game,
so it doesn't count?

28:43.960 --> 28:46.000
Does she think it's a game,
so she can toy with someone's heart?

28:46.280 --> 28:47.120
Who shot this?

28:48.000 --> 28:50.720
That's not important.
I just want to know,

28:50.800 --> 28:52.840
when did I become
an in-game couple with you?

28:53.600 --> 28:55.680
I had no idea you were also playing
"A Chinese Ghost Story."

28:57.400 --> 29:01.520
Fine, keep faking it, Huantian Xidi.

29:02.600 --> 29:03.440
What did you say?

29:04.200 --> 29:06.800
Are you surprised that I know your handle?

29:09.200 --> 29:13.040
You think Huantian Xidi
is my handle in the game?

29:16.120 --> 29:16.960
Are you Weiguang?

29:17.960 --> 29:19.280
You don't deny it now?

29:21.040 --> 29:23.840
You're wrong. I'm not Huantian Xidi.

29:25.120 --> 29:27.400
You're not? Then who are you?

29:27.480 --> 29:29.440
Wait, no, who's Huantian Xidi?

29:31.240 --> 29:32.600
I'm not telling you.

29:33.000 --> 29:34.360
But I want to know,

29:34.720 --> 29:36.560
what did you do in the game last night?

29:37.680 --> 29:39.440
Did she give you a sword?

29:40.160 --> 29:42.600
And you? What did you do?

29:45.400 --> 29:46.240
I...

29:47.760 --> 29:51.280
Fine, don't answer me. I think I know.

29:59.840 --> 30:03.440
I have a question for you, Cao Guang.

30:04.080 --> 30:04.920
Go ahead.

30:05.720 --> 30:07.640
If I was Huantian Xidi,

30:08.280 --> 30:10.320
and Huantian Xidi was Bei Weiwei,

30:11.040 --> 30:15.040
why would you play dumb
and continue to be with Huantian Xidi,

30:15.360 --> 30:18.600
after the entire school found out
about me and Xiao Nai?

30:24.040 --> 30:26.960
You said you liked me,

30:27.880 --> 30:31.120
yet you smear my name
and doubt me again and again.

30:32.120 --> 30:33.800
Is this what it means to like someone?

30:37.640 --> 30:39.920
I'm telling you in all earnest,
Cao Guang,

30:41.120 --> 30:42.760
I don't like you at all.

30:44.280 --> 30:47.360
I never did, and I never will.

30:48.680 --> 30:52.240
Please stay away from me and my friend.

30:53.560 --> 30:56.800
I don't want to waste my time,
again and again,

30:56.880 --> 30:57.960
to restore your worldview.

31:00.080 --> 31:01.800
If you're not Huantian Xidi,

31:02.320 --> 31:04.000
how did you know I'm Weiguang?

31:04.200 --> 31:05.720
How did you know she gave me a sword?

31:07.280 --> 31:09.480
I'm not telling you how I found out,

31:09.920 --> 31:12.520
nor would I tell you who Huantian Xidi is.

31:13.680 --> 31:15.040
A guy like you,

31:15.120 --> 31:17.840
who always judges others
from your subjective perspective,

31:18.680 --> 31:22.080
a minute with you is a minute too long.

31:29.400 --> 31:32.120
I sent someone to find out your handle.

31:32.200 --> 31:33.440
How could I be wrong?

31:34.360 --> 31:37.280
If it's not you, then who is it?

31:41.000 --> 31:43.800
No way! It can't be!

32:26.560 --> 32:27.480
What's wrong?

32:29.440 --> 32:32.760
I ran into Cao Guang
outside Xiaoyang's apartment.

32:34.160 --> 32:37.880
He thought Erxi was me, in the game.

32:39.560 --> 32:42.680
That's why he thought
you and him were an in-game couple?

32:44.120 --> 32:48.400
That's right.
I don't know how he got it mixed up.

32:49.720 --> 32:52.600
Erxi is really fond of Weiguang
in the game.

32:53.880 --> 32:57.440
She must have found out
Cao Guang thought she was me.

32:58.160 --> 32:59.880
That's why she's so mad.

33:00.240 --> 33:02.040
It's never been about the Xiaoyus.

33:03.760 --> 33:07.440
I had it all wrong. What do I do now?

33:08.440 --> 33:10.720
I kept calling her all morning,
but she never answered.

33:14.240 --> 33:17.280
She'll think it through.
It's not your fault.

33:18.960 --> 33:20.400
Let's hope so.

33:55.200 --> 34:00.320
Are you there, Erxi?
I want to talk to you.

34:15.199 --> 34:19.199
I'll let you calm down
and come back tomorrow.

35:15.720 --> 35:17.120
Hello? Hi, who's this?

35:18.000 --> 35:19.000
This is Xiao Nai.

35:19.880 --> 35:22.320
Xiao Nai? How did you get my number?

35:24.200 --> 35:25.200
I have my ways.

35:26.480 --> 35:28.320
Did you call to show off
how great you are?

35:29.880 --> 35:32.000
I called to fix the mess you created.

35:32.680 --> 35:35.960
Tonight at ten,
see you at the school basketball court.

35:58.160 --> 35:59.000
You're late.

36:00.880 --> 36:01.880
You're lucky I came.

36:27.480 --> 36:29.760
If you still can't figure things out,

36:30.480 --> 36:32.800
maybe you shouldn't be known as the genius
of Foreign Languages Department.

36:35.320 --> 36:37.720
- What's Bei Weiwei's handle?
- You don't need to know that.

36:38.960 --> 36:40.440
But it's not the one you thought.

36:41.080 --> 36:42.440
Who is Huantian Xidi anyway?

36:42.760 --> 36:45.080
I'm not here to give you answers.

36:46.000 --> 36:47.760
The video came from
Meng Yiran's roommate.

36:48.440 --> 36:50.000
Take care of it ASAP.

36:50.440 --> 36:53.080
I don't ever want to hear
hurtful rumors about Weiwei.

37:00.040 --> 37:02.600
Also, as a man,

37:04.000 --> 37:05.880
do not let two girls' friendship

37:06.520 --> 37:07.880
be ruined over your stupidity.

37:11.480 --> 37:14.160
Didn't you doubt Bei Weiwei,
after seeing the video?

37:14.240 --> 37:15.280
You really trust her that much?

37:18.520 --> 37:22.240
She's my girl. Why wouldn't I trust her?

37:40.800 --> 37:41.640
Cao Guang,

37:43.800 --> 37:45.720
If I was Huantian Xidi,

37:46.360 --> 37:48.320
and Huantian Xidi was Bei Weiwei,

37:49.080 --> 37:53.200
why would you play dumb
and continue to be with Huantian Xidi,

37:53.360 --> 37:56.680
after the entire school found out
about me and Xiao Nai?

38:02.120 --> 38:05.120
You said you liked me,

38:05.920 --> 38:09.080
yet you smear my name
and doubt me again and again.

38:10.200 --> 38:11.880
Is this what it means to like someone?

38:15.960 --> 38:17.960
I'm telling you in all earnest,
Cao Guang,

38:19.320 --> 38:20.840
I don't like you at all.

38:22.080 --> 38:25.280
I never did, and I never will.

38:26.880 --> 38:30.440
Please stay away from me and my friend.

38:31.880 --> 38:34.800
I don't want to waste my time,
again and again,

38:34.880 --> 38:36.160
to restore your worldview.

39:00.040 --> 39:01.280
It's a gift for you.

39:01.800 --> 39:03.840
I finally get to do something for you.

39:04.560 --> 39:07.080
Are you so moved, that you could cry?

39:07.160 --> 39:08.560
You can call it Weiguang.

39:08.640 --> 39:09.960
Or you can call it Huanxi.

39:11.000 --> 39:14.160
You can also call it Huanxi Weiguang.

39:14.800 --> 39:17.920
I made it myself, after putting so much
into blacksmithing.

39:18.480 --> 39:19.800
I'm super lucky, too.

39:19.880 --> 39:22.960
I got OP equipment at the first try.
It's for you.

39:52.720 --> 39:53.680
Zhao Erxi!

39:56.720 --> 39:58.120
How did you know I'd be here?

39:58.440 --> 40:01.480
Weren't you always bragging about
interning at Zhenyi?

40:01.560 --> 40:02.720
How you get paid 150 a day?

40:03.760 --> 40:06.200
Why are you here?
I'm not feeding your cat anymore.

40:06.360 --> 40:09.520
It's not about the cat.
I came to apologize.

40:10.640 --> 40:14.240
Apologize? For what?

40:14.920 --> 40:18.280
Zhao Erxi, I just found out
you're Huantian Xidi.

40:18.360 --> 40:20.840
I was mistaken. I'm sorry.

40:23.360 --> 40:24.760
How did you know...

40:26.480 --> 40:29.640
- Yesterday, Bei Weiwei--
- Enough!

40:30.080 --> 40:32.080
Since you know you were mistaken,

40:32.160 --> 40:33.400
from now on,

40:33.640 --> 40:36.040
go court Weiwei on your own.
Don't come to me.

40:36.600 --> 40:39.080
I'm not her maid, or your matchmaker.

40:39.320 --> 40:41.520
Please don't ever let me see you again.

40:41.600 --> 40:44.600
No, Erxi, I'm really sorry.
I only came to apologize.

40:46.160 --> 40:47.960
I mixed things up,

40:48.160 --> 40:49.720
and I hurt you in the end.

40:56.320 --> 41:00.760
I only have one question for you,
Cao Guang.

41:02.080 --> 41:08.040
Did Weiguang ever feel anything
for Huantian Xidi?

41:17.720 --> 41:19.400
I always thought you were Weiwei.

41:25.560 --> 41:27.680
How did the video in my phone vanish?

41:28.160 --> 41:30.840
Did you delete it by accident?

41:30.920 --> 41:34.520
I don't think so.
Did you push the wrong button?

41:38.920 --> 41:42.680
Erxi, I always thought
you were a good girl.

41:44.360 --> 41:45.520
A very good friend.

41:47.640 --> 41:49.400
Who wants to be your friend?

44:19.120 --> 44:21.560
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
